abomo Vilakazi (amụrụ na 27 Julaị 1978), ma ọ bụ naanị dị ka Kabomo, bụ onye na-eme ihe nkiri na onye na-agụ egwu na South Africa.
A maara ya nke ọma maka ọrụ ya n'ihe nkiri telivishọn: Zabalaza, Sink na Seriously Single
Ewezuga ime  nkiri, ọ bụkwa onye edemede, onye na-ede uri, onye nchịkọta akụkọ, onye egwu, onye na-eti egwu, onye mmepụta na onye njikwa ihe nkiri.
A mụrụ ya na 27 Julaị 1978 na Benoni, Gauteng.
E wepụtara egwu mbụ nke Kabomo, "Uzobuya", n'afọ 2012

Ihe ịga nke ọma bịara na abọm abụọ, All Things Grey na Sekusile N'ihe nkiri ncha Zabalaza, ọ rụrụ obere ọrụ, nke dugara n'ọkpụkpọ òkù ka ọ rụọ ọrụ dị mkpa na Vuzu sitcom Check Coast na 2014. N'afọ 2015, ọ pụtara na ihe nkiri Sink, mgbe ahụ na usoro telivishọn Sober Companion, nke sochiri ya bu ngosi ndị a ma ama dị ka Soul City, Scandal, Thola, Saints & Sinners, Umlilo, Captain Bozaa na Tshisa.

Dị ka onye na-ede egwu, o mere ọtụtụ egwu a ma ama maka ndị na-agụ egwu: Tshepo Tshola, Unathi, Aya, Kelly Khumalo, Thiwe, Nothende, Flabba, The Fridge, Flatoe, Pebbles, Zubz, Dineo Moeketsi. O duzikwara ihe nkiri abụọ: Droplets na Melody
Ka ọ dịgodị, o dekwara edemede maka usoro ihe nkiri Sepedi SABC1 a ma ama Skeem Sam. Otú ọ dị, ndị ọrụ ihe nkiri Droplets mechara katọọ ya na-ekwu na ọ kwụghị ha ụgwọ.
N'ọnwa Ọgọstụ 2020, ọ pụtara na ihe nkiri na-atọ ọchị Seriously Single nke Katleho Ramaphakela na Rethabile Ramaphakala duziri. A tọhapụrụ ya na 31 Julaị 2020 na Netflix.
